      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Key value store",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Key value store",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "56dowc3NW9P6NuugXZgu_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 531.7064819335938,
      "y": 254.66415405273438,
      "width": 729.779541015625,
      "height": 700,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 96300151,
      "version": 563,
      "versionNonce": 819051545,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781416076994,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Requirements:\n\nQ. key value store similar to Redis or cassandra\nA. yes\n\nQ. Max Size of key and value\nA. key : KBs\nvalue : GBs\n\nQ. partion tolerance, what do we want to prefer consitentcy or availability\nA. should be configurable\n\nQ. Any other requirements?\nA. no\n\nQ. DAU?\nA. 100 millions\n\nFunctional req:\n- Design a key value store with get and put function\n- it should supports KBs of key and upto GBs of value\n\nNFR\n- Highly available\n- Scalable\n- Low latency\n- tunable consistency\n- Fault tolerant",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Requirements:\n\nQ. key value store similar to Redis or cassandra\nA. yes\n\nQ. Max Size of key and value\nA. key : KBs\nvalue : GBs\n\nQ. partion tolerance, what do we want to prefer consitentcy or availability\nA. should be configurable\n\nQ. Any other requirements?\nA. no\n\nQ. DAU?\nA. 100 millions\n\nFunctional req:\n- Design a key value store with get and put function\n- it should supports KBs of key and upto GBs of value\n\nNFR\n- Highly available\n- Scalable\n- Low latency\n- tunable consistency\n- Fault tolerant",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SPhStoLyP6YAu4jMbls1M",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 524.865478515625,
      "y": 1036.65185546875,
      "width": 514.19970703125,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1206685849,
      "version": 210,
      "versionNonce": 1229899863,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781413864455,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Back of the envelop\n\ntraffic\n100 * 10^6 / 10^5 = 1000 rps\nGrowth 10 %\npeak rps = 5x = 5000 rps\n\nstorage\n100 * 10^6 users * ( depends on the data we store)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Back of the envelop\n\ntraffic\n100 * 10^6 / 10^5 = 1000 rps\nGrowth 10 %\npeak rps = 5x = 5000 rps\n\nstorage\n100 * 10^6 users * ( depends on the data we store)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
