      "text": "Replication Factor\nDefine replication factor = n for replicating data across multiple nodes\nhow?\nSingle leader\nMulti leader\nLeaderless ( preferred)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Replication Factor\nDefine replication factor = n for replicating data across multiple nodes\nhow?\nSingle leader\nMulti leader\nLeaderless ( preferred)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
