      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781490960972,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Anti-Entropy Repair\nWhat if replicas permanently drift apart?\n\nEntropy:\n\nEntropy means disorder.\nReplicas diverging:\nA ≠ B ≠ C\nis entropy.\n\nRepairing divergence:\nA = B = C\nis anti-entropy.\n\nThrough batch processing",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Anti-Entropy Repair\nWhat if replicas permanently drift apart?\n\nEntropy:\n\nEntropy means disorder.\nReplicas diverging:\nA ≠ B ≠ C\nis entropy.\n\nRepairing divergence:\nA = B = C\nis anti-entropy.\n\nThrough batch processing",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
